{
  "stem": "13981.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was it-- uh-- Judg-- yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The courtroom-- it was the very same courtroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the-- of course, filmmakers have to have their own script.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And they have to have their own characters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I personally was not very well satisfied with, with the picture.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, other people may have had different--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it wasn't what I had experienced.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that's hard to describe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You went into the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To the left were the-- was the prisoner dock-- docket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And immediately adjacent to them was the place where the interpreters worked There were eight interpreters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And across from the prisoners was the bench for the judges.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The eight judges were seated there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right in front of the prisoners was there defense-- were their defense lawyers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] across from the defense lawyers, in front of the judges, were the court reporters and court stenographers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] right angle to that, facing-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] let's put it this way-- there was the prosecution.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The person who was the prosecutor at any particular moment had the judges on his right side and the prisoners, or the accused, on the left side.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Behind him were the various tables and desks where the prosecution sat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Each prosecution had their own table.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and behind those is where the, the observers were-- they-- the press, on the bottom floor the press, and the visitors' gallery-- gallery.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't in the court all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in court only when needed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But sometimes, I sat with the Russian prosecution.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
